quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  50,27,"Owashe aliboola “ Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, esie shindamukosia tawe halali ye yali mubukori obwa ehale"
  50,28,"Nyasaye aliboola mbu: “ mulasolana imbeli wanje tawe, ndamala okhubarumila amekanyilisio.”"
  50,29,"Liumaho likalukhanibwa imbeli wanje tawe, ne esie shekholelanga Abasumba banje obubii tawe"
  50,30,"Inyanga yakhulireba Jahanam mbu “ Witsuule ?” nayo ilikalusia mbu : “ Abaandi baliwo umete?”"
  50,31,Ne (Janna) mwikulu ilisitibwa hambi khu baria Nyasaye
  50,32,Kano niko kalakwa khuyesiyesi ukalukha khu Nyasaye mana niyelinda
  50,33,"Ulia waria Nyasaye khukefisile, mana niyetsa nende omwoyo omulunjifu"
  50,34,Injilimwo nomulembe ino ni inyanga eyilaliwa tawe
  50,35,Balinyoolamwo shiosishiosi shiabeenya ne khuli nende bishilakhwo
  50,36,"Ne nibenga bakhwasishia imbeli wabu, abali nende amaani okhushila bano! mana nibayiya khushialo muno. koo banyolakhwo abelushila"
  50,37,Toto mu yako khulimwo nende eshitsulisio khu ulia uli nomwoyo nohomba owareka eshirwi naye alolanga
  50,38,"Ne toto khwaloonga likulu nende eshialo nende biosi bilimwo khutsinyanga tsisasaba, ne shikhwanyoola obuchonyi bwosibwosi tawe"
  50,39,Wisumilisie khukababoolanga ne witsomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi eliuba nilishili okhurula nende nilishili okhukwa
  50,40,Ne omwitsomiekhwo khandi eshilo nende niwakhamala okhumwinamila (okhusujuda)
  50,41,Ne rechelesia inyanga yomulaanji alilanjilia ahambi
  50,42,"Inyangayabaliwulilaoluyokalwomulango kwa toto, eyo niyo inyanga yokhulamusibwa"
  50,43,"Toto efwe nefwe balamusinjia nende bafwisinjia, ne ewefu namulikalukha"
  50,44,"Inyanga yeshialo shiliatikha lwangu lwangu, okhukhung’asibwa okho khuliba okhwangu khifwe"
  50,45,"Efwe khumanyile muno kababoolanga, ne ewe shobarukanga na amani tawe. Ne wikhoonyele Ikuran okhwitsulisia balia abaria inyanga yeyindukho"
  51,1,Nditsuba khu muyeka (imbumbuyeka) kusalaasinjia
  51,2,Nende kuchinganga emisiiko
  51,3,Nende kuwutsanga khubwangu
  51,4,Kukabaanga shinga kulomesibwe
  51,5,Toto kamulakungwa nikahabwene
  51,6,Ne toto inyanga yomurungo ilibaho
  51,7,Nditsuba khulikulu lilinende tsinjila
  51,8,Toto enywe muli mumakhuwa kawukhaane
  51,9,Ukalukhanibwa okhurula khubwatoto akalukhanibwa
  51,10,Abachishi balisishibwa
  51,11,Balia bakoyanila mubusilu
  51,12,"Barebanga mbu: , ni lina inyanga yomurungo"
  51,13,Inyanga eyo balinyoola eshinyasio shiomulilo
  51,14,"Pile\teshinyasio\tshienyu\tshino, nishoshamwayungubalilanga"
  51,15,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda nende tsisebele
  51,16,"Nebalinyoola ka Nyasaye abahele, toto abo bali bamalayi"
  51,17,Bakonanga hatiti eshilo
  51,18,Ne ishilo nibutsia okhushia balamanga nibasaba eshileshelo
  51,19,Ne mumiandu chiabu omukabo kwa basabi nende balasabanga kwalimwo
  51,20,Ne khushialo khulikhwo nende ebimanyisilio khubasuubila toto
  51,21,"Ne khu mibili chienyu, “koo shimulolangakhwo tawe?”"
  51,22,"Ne mwikulu kuliyo omukabo kwenyu, nende kamulakungwa"
  51,23,"Kho nditsuba khu Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, mbu toto kano nikahabwene shinga enywe muboolanga"
  51,24,Koo lwakhuulilakhwo olukano lwa bacheni ba Ibrahim boluyali
  51,25,"Olwa benjila ewuwe niboola mbu: “ Mulembe” Naye nabakalusia mbu: “Mulembe muno Abandu bengorerwe”"
  51,26,"Natsia khubandu be, niyetsa nende eshimosi shianera"
  51,27,"Nabasitilia hambi eshiakhulia, nabareba mbu: “shimulia tawe ?”"
  51,28,"Naba noburi khubo, nibamuboolela mbu “olaria tawe ” ne nibamulaka Omusiani Omuchesi"
  51,29,"Nilwa Omukhasi wuwe yabachoma, nawuka niyepama obweni naboola mbu: “ Esie omushiele mana omukumba ndakhebula endie? ”"
  51,30,"nibaboola mbu: “ endio nilwakali nilwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi oboolele, toto niye Owamachesi muno Omumanyi po"